OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FThe aunt of a woman murdered by an ex-
OL,8,Fpartner has said she is "incredibly
OL,9,Fproud" that domestic abuse specialists
OL,10,Fwill be embedded in 12 more 999
OL,11,Fcontrol rooms.
OL,13,FNour Norris, whose niece Raneem Oudeh,
OL,14,F22, and sister Khaola Saleem, 49, were
OL,15,Fmurdered by Ms Oudeh's ex-partner in
OL,16,F2018, said the scheme "gives me hope
OL,17,Fthat other families may be spared the
OL,18,Fheartbreak that ours live with every
OL,19,Fday".
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@FO]xD@WOU{D@DO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
