OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FThe latest expansion of the scheme
OL,8,Fbrings the total number of control
OL,9,Frooms staffed by specialists to 17,
OL,10,Fincluding those of Derbyshire and
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police.
OL,13,FThe Home Office has pledged that,
OL,14,Funder Raneem's Law, domestic abuse
OL,15,Fspecialists will be deployed across
OL,16,Fevery police force in England and
OL,17,FWales by 2029.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FAn inquest found mistakes made by West
OL,8,FMidlands Police (WMP) had "materially
OL,9,Fcontributed" to the women's deaths at
OL,10,Fthe hands of Janbaz Tarin.
OL,12,FTarin, who was 21 at the time of the
OL,13,Fattack on Northdown Road, Solihull,
OL,14,Fwas jailed for life in December 2018
OL,15,Fwith a minimum term of 32 years.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FOn the night of the murders, Ms Oudeh
OL,8,Fhad called WMP four times to register
OL,9,Fconcerns for her safety, and the force
OL,10,Fhad previously responded to 10
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse incidents linked to the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FFive officers were disciplined over
OL,15,Fthe failures, which Ms Oudeh's family
OL,16,Fdescribed as "beyond imagination".
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FThe experts' duties include giving
OL,8,Fadvice to officers responding to
OL,9,Fincidents on the ground, reviewing
OL,10,Fincoming domestic abuse cases and
OL,11,Ftheir risk assessments, and listening
OL,12,Fin to live calls before giving
OL,13,Ffeedback to call handlers.
OL,15,FThey also train force control room
OL,16,Fstaff on domestic abuse and support
OL,17,Fthe use of technology, including
OL,18,Fresponding to victims with a video
OL,19,Fcall.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FMs Norris said: "When my sister Khaola
OL,8,Fand my niece Raneem called for help,
OL,9,Fthey should have been heard,
OL,10,Funderstood and protected. Instead, our
OL,11,Ffamily lost two beautiful lives in
OL,12,Fcircumstances that should never have
OL,13,Fhappened.
OL,15,F"Every step forward for Raneem's Law
OL,16,Fis deeply emotional for me because it
OL,17,Fcomes from unimaginable pain and loss.
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,F"Knowing that 12 more police forces
OL,8,Fwill have domestic abuse specialists
OL,9,Fin their 999 control rooms gives me
OL,10,Fhope that other families may be spared
OL,11,Fthe heartbreak that ours live with
OL,12,Fevery day.
OL,14,F"Raneem's Law is more than a policy.
OL,15,FIt is a legacy built on love for my
OL,16,Fsister and niece and on the
OL,17,Fdetermination that their voices, and
OL,18,Fthe voices of all victims of domestic
OL,19,Fabuse, are never ignored again.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,F"I am incredibly proud to see this
OL,8,Fexpansion and remain committed to
OL,9,Fensuring that every victim who reaches
OL,10,Fout for help is met with
OL,11,Funderstanding, expertise and, most
OL,12,Fimportantly, protection."
OL,14,FNatalie Fleet, minister for
OL,15,Fsafeguarding and violence against
OL,16,Fwomen and girls, said: "Last year, one
OL,17,Fin eight women experienced domestic
OL,18,Fabuse, sexual assault, or stalking. No
OL,19,Fsociety that tolerates this level of
OL,20,Fviolence can claim to be safe for
OL,21,Fwomen.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@YO]xD@XOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782454689
OL,3,CMurder victims' relative welcomes more
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse help in 999 control
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,F"That's why we are rolling out the
OL,8,Fpioneering Raneem's Law to another 12
OL,9,Fpolice forces in England and Wales,
OL,10,Fbecause every victim ` no matter where
OL,11,Fthey live ` should be able to rely on
OL,12,Fa system that truly supports them.
OL,14,F"But we will not stop there. We will
OL,15,Fdeploy the full power of the state to
OL,16,Fmake this country safe for women and
OL,17,Fgirls."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
